Text: FW a chance to speak Cc I have scheduled you for PM on Tuesday the th of June If that does not work for you please let me know Vince cannot meet on Wednesday he has an all day PRC meeting Thursday might work if Tuesday does not Thanks Shirley Crenshaw email Original Message From Kaminski Vince J Sent Friday June AM To Mandelker Jeannie Cc Crenshaw Shirley Subject RE a chance to speak Jeannie No problem please call Shirley to set up a meeting Vince Original Message From Mandelker Jeannie Sent Friday June AM To Kaminski Vince J Subject a chance to speak Vince you may remember me as the writer who helped on the natural gas chapter for the Risk Management book As you know I work for Enron fulltime as a writer of many articles and publications I will be in Houston next week and I wondered if you had a half hour on Tuesday afternoon or Wednesday to talk about market trends Im also available until am on Thursday Thanks Jeannie

Cake for Stinson and Kateeveryone As you probably know today is Kate Lucas and Stinson Gibners last day We want to let them know we will miss them and send them off with all good wishes We will have cake this afternoon after the PRC meeting at PM in C See you then Shirley

RE Call With Vince Cc quite welcome Have a great weekend Shirley Original Message From McDermott Martin Sent Friday June AM To Crenshaw Shirley Subject Call With Vince thanks for organizing that for me I await his call on Monday London time cheers Martin Martin McDermott Enron Credit Manager Ph Fax Mob
Invoice to be approved and Computer order to be approvedI have forwarded several invoices to you for approval and also the computer order to replace the one they took for Rusty Parks Thanks Shirley

FW Followup on CA energy crisis infoCan you let me know the answer to what she is asking Thanks Original Message From Thome Jennifer Sent Tuesday May PM To Crenshaw Shirley Subject RE Followup on CA energy crisis info Shirley One more question could you please let me know the date and event from which Vince picked up these handouts Thanks Jennifer

Vince Kaminskis Itinerary for June th Cc Ian Vince will be arriving in Philadelphia Wednesday evening the th of June He will be at Wharton during the day on the th returning to Houston the evening of the th He is staying at the Inn at Penn the night of the th If you need anything else please let me know Regards Shirley Crenshaw Original Message From Kaminski Vince J Sent Tuesday June AM To MacMillan Ian ENRON Cc Crenshaw Shirley Kaminski Vince J Subject RE Strategic Management Society Conference Ian I shall come to Wharton on Thursday June meeting with Howard Kunreuther I shall ask my assistant to forward you my itinerary I shall also register for the October Conference Thanks for reminding me Vince Original Message From MacMillan Ian ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESMacMillanCIanCmacmilliwhartonEupennEeduE NRONcom Sent Tuesday June AM To Cc Rita Mcgrath Email Boisot Max Subject Strategic Management Society Conference A couple of months ago you agreed to serve on a panel on real options that Rita McGrath at Columbia had assembled We have been informed that you have not registered for the conference in SFO October to Can you please register they are getting antsy about it Go to When are you due at Wharton again

Wednesday June th MidYear Review Cc Just a reminder that this Wednesday June th is the MidYear Review It will be held in the th Floor Boardroom from PM and lunch will be brought in around AM The HR people that will be there are Anne Labbe Amanda Kaminski and Cindy Skinner
Wednesday Luncheoneveryone There will not be a Lunch tomorrow June th as the Research Group will be in their PRC Meeting See you next week Shirley

INDOAmerican Chamber of Commerce Gala and Dinner June Cc On behalf of Enron and the Research Group Vince purchased a table at the subject event There are places at the table and he would like to invite you and your wife to attend The attendees from the Research Group will be Vasant Shanbhogue and his wife Vasants wife is actually working on the event so her place will not be counted in with our group Krishna Krishnarao and his wife Sandeep Kohli and his wife Maureen Raymond Please let me know if you are available on the th Shirley

IndoAmerican Chamber of Commerce of Greater Houston Gala On behalf of Vince Kaminski and Enron Corp a check in the amount of is being mailed to you today to purchase a friends table for the June th gala A list of the attendees will be forthcoming Best Regards Shirley Crenshaw Administrative Coordinator Enron Research Group email
